GitHub Repository Post Introduction:

Welcome to my GitHub repository for the Recipe Organizer project! In this repository, you'll find all the code and resources used to create a web-based recipe organizer application. This project is part of my internship with CodTech IT Solutions, where I was assigned the task of developing a recipe organizer using CSS, HTML, and JavaScript.

Tools Used:

1. HTML: Used for structuring the web pages and organizing content.
2. CSS: Used for styling and formatting the user interface of the application.
3. JavaScript: Used for adding interactivity and dynamic features to the application.
4. Bootstrap: Utilized the Bootstrap framework for responsive design and layout components.
5. jQuery: Incorporated jQuery for simplifying DOM manipulation and event handling.
6. Font Awesome: Integrated Font Awesome for adding scalable vector icons to the application.

